article_title: Delta Air Lines Orders 15 Airbus A321s
article_text:
Delta Air Lines Inc. on Monday said it ordered 15 A321 aircraft from Airbus Group NV for delivery beginning in 2018.

The order is valued at about $1.65 billion, based...
